<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>州を選択してください</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .state-selection-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px;
      padding: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa, #b2ebf2);
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .state-selection-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #00796b;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .state-selection-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #004d40;
    }

    .back-button {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .back-button button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #00796b;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .back-button button:hover {
      background-color: #004d40;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="state-selection-container">
    <h1 class="state-selection-title">州が選択されていません。</h1>
    <p class="state-selection-subtitle">特に指定がない場合は "指定しない" を選択してください。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="back-button">
    <!-- ボタンで前のページに戻る -->
    <button onclick="history.back()">戻る</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

